Hello everybody its SilentStrikes (DemApplez) here with another avicus network video. My last video got a good amount of views and I have another video here. Subscribe for more of these everyday as I have recorded many episodes, gameplay, and commentaries that I am waiting to release. 

Here is my second episode: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIaB1e9fag4





Check out all of my other videos here and leave feedback on the forums or the comment section :) I hope to see you around the network!
